"""Test the Dictionary Tagger on unicode combining characters.

             These introduce space within normalized token text.
             """
dt = CiDictCemTagger()
self.assertEqual([(u'Novel', None), (u'imidazoý1,2-a¨pyridine', u'B-CM'), (
    u'and', None), (u'imidazoý1,2-b¨pyridazine', u'B-CM'), (u'derivatives',
    None)], dt.tag(['Novel', 'imidazoý1,2-a¨pyridine', 'and',
    'imidazoý1,2-b¨pyridazine', 'derivatives']))
